## üéØ Overview

This project demonstrates a complete serverless architecture using AWS SAM (Serverless Application Model). The entire infrastructure - including Lambda functions, API Gateway, DynamoDB table, and IAM roles - is defined in a single `template.yaml` file and deployed with just two commands.

## üèóÔ∏è Architecture

```
Client Request
     ‚Üì
API Gateway (REST API)
     ‚Üì
Lambda Functions (Python 3.11)
     ‚Üì
DynamoDB (NoSQL Database)
```

The application follows a serverless microservices pattern where each Lambda function handles a specific operation (Create, Read, Update, Delete).

