## üí∞ Cost Optimization

This architecture is cost-effective because:
- **Lambda:** Free tier includes 1M requests/month
- **DynamoDB:** Pay-per-request pricing, no idle costs
- **API Gateway:** Pay only for API calls made
- **No servers:** Zero compute costs when not in use

**Estimated cost for development:** < $1/month

## üîí Security

- Lambda functions have minimal IAM permissions (least privilege)
- DynamoDB access restricted to specific Lambda roles
- API endpoints can be secured with API keys or Cognito (not implemented)
- All traffic encrypted in transit (HTTPS)

